# Caddy reverse proxy with automatic HTTPS (Let's Encrypt).
# The domain comes from the DOMAIN environment variable (set on the caddy
# service in docker-compose.prod.yml) — no manual editing needed. Caddy
# terminates TLS and forwards to the frontend (nginx), which serves the SPA and
# proxies /api, /uploads, /l/ to the backend.
# Requires: DNS A record for $DOMAIN -> this host, ports 80 + 443 open.
{$DOMAIN} {
    reverse_proxy z-chat-frontend:80
}
